                            +-------------------------+
                            |My Neighbor Totoro (1988)|
                            +-------------------------+

+--------------+
|Plot/Storyline|
+--------------+

Two young girls, Satsuke and her younger sister Mei, move into a house in the country with their father to be closer to their hospitalized mother. Satsuke and Mei discover that the nearby forest is inhabited by magical spirits called Totoros (pronounced toe-toe-ro). They soon befriend these Totoros, and have several wonderous adventures.

+-------+
|Details|
+-------+

- Contains Feature Film &amp; DVD Menu, Fullscreen Format

- Originally titled &quot;Tonari no Totoro&quot; and directed by Hayao Miyazaki

- Originally released April 16th, 1988 in Japan

- Genres: Animation, Adventure, Family, Fantasy

- Rated G - Suitable for all audiences

- This is the re-released English-dubbed NTSC-formatted version produced by 20th Century Fox on December 3rd, 2002

- English language audio track ONLY, includes English subtitles

